年的參賽佳麗質素甚高，不但每位都長得很漂亮，就連身材亦是令女人也自愧不如的完美。身高180cm的冠軍佳麗Ruethaipreeya Nuangle身材比例極佳，胸以下全是大長腿，膚白貌美勁有氣質。再加上她是一名大學高材生，就讀於泰國Sukhothai Thammathirat文學院，獲不少網民大讚很有氣質，舉手投足都充滿優雅感。<br />\n<br />\n不過亦有人質疑她為何能得到冠軍，更批評她長得確實不及亞軍佳麗Thanyada Kunpaipuen及季軍佳麗Patchara Sripattanakul，認為她們更有資格奪得「蒂芬妮環球小姐」后冠，為她們大感可惜。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：趙允琳<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/355395/27%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E9%AB%98%E6%9D%90%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%AA%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E7%BE%8E%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D-%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E6%A5%B5%E4%BD%B3%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F355395%2F27%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%259D%2590%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%259D%2590%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B3%25AA&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=3f326cda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/355395/27%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E9%AB%98%E6%9D%90%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%AA%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E7%BE%8E%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D-%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E6%A5%B5%E4%BD%B3%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA</a>"},{"pid":"4b5a293f9832a1a504a032dd97e5e6ffbcd637c9","tid":1392752,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"somi咁"},{"pid":"ba454c8aab20f47a5004de33f7fc613caf21aad0","tid":1392752,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"有冇變性前既圖?"},{"pid":"c90be1cc785126fa0a033bc2bfc08c63230228ba","tid":1392752,"uid":224272,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"rep